short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: make 'Table Of Contents(TOC)' to highlight current position and provide some additional guidance

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
In RestDoc pages, there are too many API endpoints and this fact makes users get lost.

 This Extension makes 'Table Of Contents(TOC)' to highlight current position. then make user to know where they are easy.

 And provide some additional guidance with Pressing "Ctrl" Key.
